{"tid":1901674,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【奶共吖啦 返武漢吖啦】26%確診個案曾涉足北角 專家籲儘量避免前往北角","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T05:21:32.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4a34023f0c347355aa8347503583a2c959ee14","tid":1901674,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200227&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60650514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200227%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60650514&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0aVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=755b5bae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200227%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60650514&h=824aed51\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200227&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60650514</a><br />\n【武漢肺炎】26%確診個案曾涉足北角 專家指須高度關注籲儘量避免前往<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://msighk.files.wordpress.com/2015/08/travel-alert.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmsighk.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F08%2Ftravel-alert.jpg&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0aVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=db51bf85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://msighk.files.wordpress.com/2015/08/travel-alert.jpg</a><br />\n有感染及傳染病科專科醫生認為，目前北角情況值得高度關注，提醒市民出入要格外小心，除非是在該區居住或工作等必須前往，否則「儘量可以嘅話唔好去住」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本港最先涉足北角的個案，是第6宗個案，一名於武漢武昌區白沙淵街市做收銀的男子，回港後確診，他在港居於北角建華街宇宙閣。之後出現北角明星海鮮酒家的飯局群組，29人出席有6人確診。除此之外，個案57及59兩名工程師同事，同於北角英皇道上班。之前確診個案69的警察，隸屬北角警署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近北角再成為疫情焦點，因北角書局街美輪大廈的福慧精捨出現超級傳播事件，至今有最少9名到過該精舍的人確診，當中個案64及65夫婦，太太曾到精舍，兩人均曾到北角皇冠大廈求診。"},{"pid":"a5fb37ded46dc04d166f935129557ddc92ad38f9","tid":1901674,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:00:13.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;"},{"pid":"3c3a2ba141c77914e8c7b410790e79d7b4e560f7","tid":1901674,"uid":332610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"唔使去果頭操野啦"}]}